title: Conor McGregor's appeal bid denied by Supreme Court of Ireland in civil sexual assault case
description: The Supreme Court of Ireland rejected McGregor's bid for further appeal after a civil jury found him liable for sexually assaulting Nikita Hand in a Dublin hotel in 2018.
